OL,3,CHospital porters secure landmark
OL,4,Cagreement to end alleged bullying
OL,5,Cdispute
OL,7,FPlanned strike action by porters
OL,8,Femployed at Southampton General
OL,9,FHospital has been suspended.
OL,11,FThe Unite Union says the workers have
OL,12,Faccepted wide-ranging proposals to end
OL,13,Fwhat it claims were 'issues of
OL,14,Fbullying and harassment.'
OL,16,FIt says the hospital has agreed to
OL,17,Fintroduce a 67-point plan.
