OL,7,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,8,Fsaid: "This is a tremendously
OL,9,Fimportant victory for a group of low
OL,10,Fpaid workers who had been systemically
OL,11,Fmistreated by management.
OL,13,F"By being prepared to stand up and be
OL,14,Fcounted, while willing to take
OL,15,Findustrial action, the porters have
OL,16,Fensured a dramatic improvement in
OL,17,Ftheir working conditions. Their
OL,18,Fbravery should be applauded."
