OL,7,FUnite regional officer Kate Attwooll
OL,8,Fsaid: "Porters are the lifeblood of
OL,9,Fthe NHS, putting patients first and
OL,10,Fconnecting with compassion and care on
OL,11,Fa daily basis.
OL,13,F"This is a group of amazing human
OL,14,Fbeings and they deserve to feel safe
OL,15,Fand valued at work. This has been an
OL,16,Fextremely challenging and complex
OL,17,Fdispute, uncovering over a decade of
OL,18,Fabuse and misconduct by management.
