OL,7,F"Unite members have stood together and
OL,8,Fsecured firm commitments from
OL,9,Fmanagement on a landmark deal covering
OL,10,Fmultiple areas of improvement for
OL,11,Fstaff.
OL,13,F"Unite will ensure that every single
OL,14,Fone of Southampton hospital's promises
OL,15,Fis upheld and acted upon.
