OL,7,F"Unite takes a zero-tolerance approach
OL,8,Fto bullying and harassment in the
OL,9,Fworkplace and we will make certain
OL,10,Fthat it is never allowed to take root
OL,11,Fat the hospital again. Now is the time
OL,12,Ffor management to deliver."
OL,14,FA spokesperson for University Hospital
OL,15,FSouthampton NHS Foundation Trust,
OL,16,Fsaid: "Following constructive
OL,17,Fdiscussions with UNITE, porters at UHS
OL,18,Fhave cancelled the planned industrial
OL,19,Faction in December and January.
