OL,7,F"With ACAS support, an agreement has
OL,8,Fbeen reached on a range of actions
OL,9,Faimed at significantly improving the
OL,10,Fexperience of our portering staff.
OL,12,F"Porters play a vital role in the safe
OL,13,Foperation of our services and patient
OL,14,Fcare. UHS is committed to
OL,15,Fcollaborating with UNITE to implement
OL,16,Fthe mutually agreed actions as a
OL,17,Fpriority, and to ensuring porters feel
OL,18,Fvalued and included across the
OL,19,Forganisation."
